            "title": "寶勝上月綜合經收淨額按年跌8.2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">寶勝國際(03813)公布，今年3月份綜合經營收益淨額14.42億元(人民幣．下同)，按年倒退8.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寶勝官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241111_FI_source-web_03818.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寶勝官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241111_FI_source-web_03818.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寶勝官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綜合經營收益淨額是指總銷售額減銷售折扣及銷售退貨的數字。至於今年首季該公司累計綜合經營收益淨額，則為51.07億元，按年減少5.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844648-%e5%af%b6%e5%8b%9d%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e7%b6%9c%e5%90%88%e7%b6%93%e6%94%b6%e6%b7%a8%e9%a1%8d%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c8-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240513_FI_source-web_03813.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 17:00:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "丘鈦上月手機攝像頭模組銷量按年降20.1% 按月則升28.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">丘鈦科技(01478)公布，今年3月份手機攝像頭模組銷量2944.2萬件，按年降20.1%，按月則升28.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"丘鈦科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/01478-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"丘鈦科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/01478-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">丘鈦科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其中3200萬像素以下攝像頭模組銷量1229.4萬件，按年大跌42.1%，按月微升0.4%；而3200萬像素及以上攝像頭模組銷量，則達1714.8萬件，按年升9.9%，按月增長達60.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他領域攝像頭模組上月銷量119.9萬件，按年及按月分別升10.3%及20.3%。攝像頭模組銷售數量合計3064.1萬件，按年降19.2%，按月則升28.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：丘鈦科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240325_FI_source-web_01478.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：丘鈦科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240325_FI_source-web_01478.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：丘鈦科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，上月攝像頭模組產品銷售數量按月增加主要是由於季節性因素；按年減少則主要因為公司繼續專注於以中高端手機攝像頭模組和其他領域攝像頭模組為核心的產品策略，而這些中高端產品銷量無論按年及按月均錄得良好增長。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指紋識別模組銷量合計1729.5萬件，按年大升95.1%，按月也增26%；其中屏下指紋識別模組銷量974萬件，按年及按月分別升46.7%及42.4%；電容式指紋識別模組銷量604.8萬件，按年大增1.72倍，按月升40.5%；超聲波指紋識別模組銷量150.7萬件。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14844594-%e4%b8%98%e9%88%a6%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e6%94%9d%e5%83%8f%e9%a0%ad%e6%a8%a1%e7%b5%84%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d20-1-%e6%8c%89%e6%9c%88%e5%89%87%e5%8d%8728-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/01478-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 16:55:33",
